Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:35.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱的幽灵旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 旅馆还没到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍忍 就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还走得真久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为度过剩下不多的夏季休日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合的地方吧 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带是任何观光指南\N都未登载的海边好地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又有点走往常的路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魑魅亭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古色苍然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形态昔古
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要住宿于此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照诸星的话做 最后一定很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的错 我可不想重复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对交给诸星来办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种破旅馆 住我家的别墅还…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由东京来的诸星及其他3名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请入内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔加入庶民的生活也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庶民的美女也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就将茶送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是客人 是客人来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下今晚就不寂寞了 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的我们家只有老太婆和我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有二人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还被这儿的女孩招待了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起她 她到哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个长发带寂寞感的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看到那女孩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年阿玉又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫阿玉是吗？那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这儿的女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打工的或…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了可不要吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿玉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿玉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 还是吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市中的人只有嘴巴硬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被你们的形象吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美丽的人是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夫妇才更像鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要发生什么不吉利的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿玉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐 我们找了你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的主人开玩笑说你是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 谁也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了 那个人没有影子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕黑 我好怕黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 让你在吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想用这样子来吓阿玉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来给你们看并注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能放磷火吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是为了什么在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一股怨气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年到了夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那夫妇都来吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为幽灵还被人吓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 非常了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那夫妇为对手 你也很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 我们帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吓怪物夫妇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我在 如同有了一百人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将头发弄乱一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是用原来面孔是赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 摆架势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是猫又
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我是座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么弄不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼军团出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我安心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就现在 出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说什么 你是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用 我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是阿玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 趁现在逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了 赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 下来是你诸星 去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又冒出一个祭品了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑我好怕 窄 我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 不要欺负我了 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼 恶魔 利己主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年夏天绝对要报此仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会更加痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵小姐 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快收拾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一大早就出现嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这么快就要回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还要住二天的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经打扰够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们服务嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后才好玩的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个 一起吓阿玉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是最后还想见次阿玉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵怎么可能一大早就出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎么可能违背常理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违背常理 实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一起去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话对大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是幽灵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好被缠上了 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放松一切 待会儿会有可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵 让那样的美人放着太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是美人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是人 是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是恶人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 为何要去海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 一定阿玉小姐对海有回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能带我去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点无法顺意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵去海水浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常理应是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违背常理实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她成为幽灵太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐 游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那告诉我住址 电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令真是的 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 拉姆 你为何跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是幽灵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍为轻心可就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对阿玉小姐太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概对海有什么迷恋 所以才不能升天的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二 二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点脸要烤伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你们 真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖气的碎片在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实刚才还和幽灵在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐说口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个幽灵并非邪恶的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请喝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃刨冰 吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是刨冰有什么伤心往事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 到底对此世间有何迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果达成心愿或许就能升天了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐 如有事我们能办我们一定帮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样…升天？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以如此 不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 想要的东西及想做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃炒面三份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没问你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会自杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻子 对方是幽灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是樱花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿燕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的年轻人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 对达令做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用理我们 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放下不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要男朋友 我想要男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为何不早说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉小姐 如我可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要小孩 不要小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 都被甩了 甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这堕落症够了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去？回那魑魅亭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,240)}海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买这个好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于没让你升天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦这么多 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么使那女孩魂魄犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:22:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿玉 回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坏的孩子 又缠着客人叫人家买的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不要一直缠着客人 快升天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人生的乐趣无法抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还无法升天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介的母亲是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连颜面也不知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对母亲的记忆只剩怀中的触感还存留
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介对母亲的记忆最后通知父亲被打开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里埋藏的真相是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 未曾谋面的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========注===========
